<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FarmConnect Agreements</title>
    <style>
        body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
}

.container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

h1, h2, h3 {
    color: #333;
}

h1 {
    text-align: center;
}

.party {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.signature {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Contract Farming Agreement</h1>
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

        <h2>Parties Involved:</h2>
        <div class="party">
            <h3>Farmer:</h3>
            <p>Name: [Farmer's Name]</p>
            <p>Address: [Farmer's Address]</p>
            <p>Contact Information: [Farmer's Phone, Email]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="party">
            <h3>Buyer/Company:</h3>
            <p>Name: [Buyer's Name]</p>
            <p>Address: [Buyer's Address]</p>
            <p>Contact Information: [Buyer's Phone, Email]</p>
        </div>

        <h2>1. Purpose of Agreement</h2>
        <p>This contract outlines the terms and conditions under which the Farmer agrees to cultivate and deliver specified crops to the Buyer.</p>

        <h2>2. Description of Produce</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Crops to be Grown:</strong> [List of crops]</li>
            <li><strong>Quantity:</strong> [Estimated quantity]</li>
            <li><strong>Quality Standards:</strong> [Specify quality requirements]</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Duration of Contract</h2>
        <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> [Start Date]</p>
        <p><strong>End Date:</strong> [End Date]</p>
        <p><strong>Renewal Terms:</strong> [Details on renewal options]</p>

        <h2>4. Pricing and Payment Terms</h2>
        <p><strong>Price per Unit:</strong> [Specify price]</p>
        <p><strong>Payment Schedule:</strong> [Details on payment timelines]</p>
        <p><strong>Method of Payment:</strong> [Cash, bank transfer, etc.]</p>

        <h2>5. Responsibilities of the Farmer</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Cultivate crops according to agreed standards.</li>
            <li>Provide regular updates on crop status.</li>
            <li>Ensure compliance with all agricultural regulations.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>6. Responsibilities of the Buyer</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Provide necessary resources (e.g., seeds, fertilizers) if agreed.</li>
            <li>Make timely payments as outlined.</li>
            <li>Assist with marketing and distribution if applicable.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Risk Management</h2>
        <p><strong>Force Majeure:</strong> Outline conditions under which the contract may be suspended.</p>
        <p><strong>Insurance:</strong> Specify if insurance is required for crops.</p>

        <h2>8. Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p>Outline procedures for handling disputes, including mediation and arbitration options.</p>

        <h2>9. Termination Clause</h2>
        <p>Conditions under which either party may terminate the contract.</p>
        <p>Notice period required for termination.</p>

        <h2>10. Signatures</h2>
        <p>By signing below, both parties agree to the terms outlined in this contract.</p>

        <div class="signature">
            <p><strong>Farmer's Signature:</strong> _______________________</p>
            <p>Date: ________________</p>
        </div>
        <div class="signature">
            <p><strong>Buyer's Signature:</strong> _______________________</p>
            <p>Date: ________________</p>
        </div>

        <h2>Additional Information</h2>
        <p><strong>Contact Support:</strong> [Support Email/Phone]</p>
        <p><strong>FAQs:</strong> [Link to FAQs]</p>
        <p><strong>Resources:</strong> [Link to resources on best practices in contract farming]</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
